R12: KEY CHANGES vs. ORIGINAL WEEKLY PROPOSAL |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R13: 1. Min deposit lowered to 15-20 CAD |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R14: Original 30 CAD min deposit is too high for daily/weekly reloads, it kills participation rates. Reload promo benchmarks in CA sit at 10-20 CAD min. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R15: 2. Sat & Sun filled in |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R16: Original calendar left Saturday & Sunday EMPTY (just NaN cells with the Friday "Weekend Boost" supposedly stretching across). This is a wasted weekend, since peak iGaming traffic is Fri-Sun. Now every day has a dedicated promo with its own opt-in (better for Customer.io segmentation, attribution, and A/B testing). |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R17: 3. Sunday Cashback added |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R18: BIGGEST recommendation. Cashback is the #1 retention tool in CA market and your original calendar has none. 10% up to 200 CAD with x1 wager is loss-recovery, not a deposit bonus - drives win-back of churning users and reduces 7-day churn significantly. Auto-credited Monday morning = strong reactivation trigger. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R19: 4. Wagering x40 → x35 |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R20: Same logic as welcome pack - aligns with CA industry average and improves clear-rate. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R21: 5. Max Win raised |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R22: Original 75 CAD max win on FS feels stingy. Bumped to 100-150 CAD on FS, 1000-1500 CAD on cash reloads. More aspirational, better social proof (winners screenshot bigger wins). |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R23: 6. Friday reload bigger |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R24: Original Friday was 30% up to 100 CAD + 60 FS. New Friday: 75% up to 300 CAD + 30 FS. Friday should be the WEEK'S BEST reload - that's when discretionary spend peaks. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R25: 7. Wednesday reload bigger |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R26: Original 40% / 120 CAD → 50% / 200 CAD + FS. Midweek dip is real; needs a stronger pull. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R27: 8. Quests preserved + cleaned |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R28: Tuesday & Thursday quests stayed (good mechanics), but trigger threshold lowered from 75 bets / 50× win to 50 bets / 30× win - more achievable, higher completion rate = higher engagement KPI. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R29: 9. Suggested Customer.io flow |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R30: Each day = own opt-in event → trigger campaign → 24h reminder if not deposited → next-day report email. Use cashback day as the weekly anchor email (highest open rate). |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R31: 10. Test ideas for month 2+ |  |  |  |  |  |  | 
R32: Once you have traffic data, test: (a) Tournament Sundays instead of cashback for high-VIP segment; (b) Drop-and-Wins from providers (Pragmatic, Evolution) layered on top - prize pool funded by provider, not you; (c) Birthday bonus + level-up bonus via lifecycle in Customer.io. |  |  |  |  |  |  | 

